2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses deep learning techniques for vehicle classification, which falls under the domain of machine learning.
3. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses a neural network (CNN) for vehicle classification, which is a subfield of neural computing.
4. cs.SD (Sound) - Although the paper deals with radar signals, which are not sound signals, the processing techniques used for signal analysis and classification can be similar to those used in sound processing.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with processing signals for vehicle classification, which can be considered as a form of multimedia analysis.
